  "remarks": "TAi.057 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Director of the Passport and Visa Department in the Ministry of Interior under the Taliban regime. Directs a Taliban \"front\"(mahaz) and serves as member of the military commission of the Taliban as of mid-2013. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on 9 July 2007, 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
